items.content_text:
### Programming Languages

*   [Move (⭐1.5k)](https://github.com/MystenLabs/awesome-move#readme) - Domain-specific programming language for writing safe smart contracts.

### Front-End Development

*   [Hydrogen (⭐170)](https://github.com/shopify/awesome-hydrogen#readme) - Edge-first framework for building Shopify storefronts with React.

### Networking

*   [Scapy (⭐295)](https://github.com/secdev/awesome-scapy#readme) - Python-based interactive packet manipulation.

### Miscellaneous

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [cycle-fav-dirs (⭐2)](https://github.com/cibinmathew/cycle-fav-dirs) - A plugin to cycle through your favourite directories.

### Completions / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [ssh-agent (bobsoppe) (⭐26)](https://github.com/bobsoppe/zsh-ssh-agent) - Manage `ssh-agent`.
*   [ssh-agent (hkupty) (⭐12)](https://github.com/hkupty/ssh-agent) - Automatically starts `ssh-agent` to set up and load whichever credentials you want for `ssh` connections.

### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [paroape (⭐3)](https://github.com/ParoaPe/ParoaPe-zsh-theme) - Based on [lpha3cho (⭐46)](https://github.com/sdcampbell/lpha3cho-Oh-My-Zsh-theme-for-pentesters)
*   [ys (⭐0)](https://github.com/cristiancavalli/ys-zsh-custom-theme) - Clean, simple, compatible and meaningful theme meant for dark backgrounds.
items.content_html:
Plugins / superconsole - Windows-only

  • cycle-fav-dirs (⭐2) - A plugin to cycle through your favourite directories.

Completions / superconsole - Windows-only

  • ssh-agent (bobsoppe) (⭐26) - Manage ssh-agent.
  • ssh-agent (hkupty) (⭐12) - Automatically starts ssh-agent to set up and load whichever credentials you want for ssh connections.

Themes / superconsole - Windows-only

  • paroape (⭐3) - Based on lpha3cho (⭐46)
  • ys (⭐0) - Clean, simple, compatible and meaningful theme meant for dark backgrounds.
